{"tid":1111151,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"邊一套異世界漫畫最好睇?","createTime":"2019-04-16T21:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T17:26:24.000Z","uid":56498,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"79043a24af77bb1f77800013e303c032c61bc2a2","tid":1111151,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T21:28:10.000Z","msg":"只討論漫畫唔講動畫<br />\n<br />\n我諗我都叫睇唔少，暫時應該最出色係 異世界叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本蜘蛛子我覺得幾好睇，但佢加左d乜唔同人格之後就變到唔知做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n哥布林殺手都好睇但係劇情開始套路化<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有咩推薦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ba40368b658f430ee9cd15ad9bec21feeb7b12","tid":1111151,"uid":6327,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T21:32:15.000Z","msg":"呢期鍾意睇d女人異世界系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公爵千金的愛好 <br />\n自稱惡役大小姐的婚約者觀察記錄 (呢套笑到on9)"},{"pid":"d6402785ca8057427e939a50cf7e2aefdce96bf2","tid":1111151,"uid":90310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T21:41:33.000Z","msg":"講套冷門少少既 傳說中勇者的結婚活動<br />\n雖然畫左一排就俾人腰斬 但係好好睇"},{"pid":"ca502c2bc340c8dc5b87b814e86530a7d3aa2499","tid":1111151,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:06:29.000Z","msg":"幼女戰記， 蜘蛛子好睇<br />\n<br />\n其他太過套路，太過FF，太過順利，套套都開後宮<br />\n<br />\n盾勇皇后出嚟即係變到唔好睇<br />\n史萊姆做魔王之後愈來愈<br />\nRe：Monster 好垃圾<br />\n<br />\n無戰轉生 睇過下，好似幾好睇"},{"pid":"bbc85f1fb2f3edbb27bfd8582191cf537b225395","tid":1111151,"uid":91725,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:32:50.000Z","msg":"異世界騎乘好好睇<br />\n騎乘之王(別名：ライドンキング)"},{"pid":"229239260b9769f7ac7bb1b13a092249b3b6837d","tid":1111151,"uid":32221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"79043a24af77bb1f77800013e303c032c61bc2a2","tid":1111151,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T21:28:10.000Z","msg":"只討論漫畫唔講動畫<br />\n<br />\n我諗我都叫睇唔少，暫時應該最出色係 異世界叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本蜘蛛子我覺得幾好睇，但佢加左d乜唔同人格之後就變到唔知做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n哥布林殺手都好睇但係劇情開始套路化<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有咩推薦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:41:29.000Z","msg":"異世界叔叔真係極品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傲嬌同宅冰女都勁正<br />\n<br />\n異世界題材寫得最好我覺得係愛書的下剋上，都有漫畫"},{"pid":"0e740f42df79c025235eb1cdbd0269ddacbf87d0","tid":1111151,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:44:38.000Z","msg":"異世界迷宮黑心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角係原世界靠炒樓炒到廿歲就發左達，之後穿越左要做社畜，主角無任何能力、屬性值極低乜都學唔到，次次想用腦發圍都衰收尾，收左班好似好勁既手下但係個個都剩係識扯主角後腳，主角成日意氣風發但係次次超展開搞到仆街，超撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/980OYur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F980OYur.png&h=30005fa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b65adb7b115d8e985eb8be3a90c13531049904bf","tid":1111151,"uid":186489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:25:27.000Z","msg":"記錄的地平線"},{"pid":"f67f300a68895178d68eba2cf81252e15a7606cb","tid":1111151,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"一定係無職轉生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9245ea30f905fa418278cc2d0065563b2ef6913b","tid":1111151,"uid":49